results.name: Theta series of A_7 lattice.
reference: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 110.
mathematica: terms = 29; f[q_] = LatticeData["A7", "ThetaSeriesFunction"][-I Log[q]/Pi]; s = Series[f[q], {q, 0, 2 terms}]; DeleteCases[CoefficientList[s, q^(1/2) ] // Round, 0][[1 ;; terms]] (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Jul 04 2017 *)
